    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are sound, and it handles well on the road. However, there are visible signs of age, including some minor exterior scratches and noticeable wear on the interior upholstery. It is a solid, honest car that prioritizes utility and dependability over cosmetic perfection.",
