    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? This car is in honest, fair condition and is ready to get you where you need to go! While it shows some expected signs of use and character from its time on the road, it remains a solid, dependable choice for anyone needing practical transportation with a positive history.",
