      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unrivaled caliber. This specimen has been maintained to an exacting standard, preserved in showroom condition with no discernible wear. Its mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation are beyond reproach, representing the pinnacle of its class for the collector who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
